{"tid":1303013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"應屆DSE考生陳浩霆遇溺亡　考獲20分母嘆未能自己拎成績","createTime":"2019-07-10T06:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T15:23:40.000Z","uid":212626,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f3dd9b41e7388e59962b95ef8f85092e5722438d","tid":1303013,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:57:16.000Z","msg":"大嶼山海迎灘昨（9 曰）遇溺死亡的18歲應屆DSE考生陳浩霆，今晨其入讀的天水圍中華基督教青年會中學為學生派發成續表，據悉，陳早前參加大學的「尖子計劃」，已獲有條件收錄；其母和胞姐替死者到學校領取成績表，母嘆道「點解唔等多一日，拎埋成績」。<br />\n<br />\n學校校長陳錦偉接受傳媒訪問時透露，陳浩霆考獲(DSE)中學文憑試成續為20分，英文科考獲5分。他又說，陳為人文靜，成績優異，為英文學會的成員。在知道他不幸遇溺感到難過，校方已啟動危機應變小組，為情緒不安的同學進行輔導，並已就事件通知教育局。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，陳浩霆的同班相屬同學心情現己平伏，並表示會為陳母製作陳同學在校的生活相簿送贈留念。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2396673/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2396673%2F&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC9VSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=b3d24f06\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2396673/</a>"},{"pid":"3051c7f3ff0a66bccbae8ee32945ad2d96a44f0f","tid":1303013,"uid":6548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:00:17.000Z","msg":"呢單慘"},{"pid":"77c3aac458f2145dcc8cf1710c15b2bdd364d2a8","tid":1303013,"uid":171684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:02:56.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3879c9a5e5b16d1732c1d13537ec9d257f9afb","tid":1303013,"uid":82938,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:03:37.000Z","msg":"準大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80be1c89aa1893377e0a95dcc4cae77f5d73f97","tid":1303013,"uid":82938,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:04:34.000Z","msg":"「點解唔等多一日，拎埋成績」。<br />\n<br />\n等多日拎完成績之後浸死又有乜用。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c76da719c44ceb3f5c0d